{"tid":423584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[short撚左]何君堯指無申回鄉證者是支持港獨　","createTime":"2017-10-04T04:31:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T04:37:07.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"99e0f61a15f3de7d9d5e85c8d76eb7d296e0984d","tid":423584,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T04:31:50.000Z","msg":"立法會議員何君堯昨晚於facebook直播時，提到有指香港現在有上百萬人沒有申請回鄉，認為這些人的心態就是「支持港獨」。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯早前到北京找朋友，並如常於晚上進行fb直播，被質疑是「翻牆」做節目。他昨晚在fb直播回應時，批評質疑者是「死蠢」，「未去過那個地方就亂咁估，你喺內地唔可用fb，但（如果）本身用兩地通電話，一樣可以上到網，可以上到fb，咁基本嘅事都唔知&hellip;&hellip;我使乜翻牆啫，我淨係畀多幾百蚊月費，我咪有呢啲服務囉！」<br />\n<br />\n何君堯之後指摘質疑者不學無術，「可能連回鄉證都無」，又提到有指香港有上百萬人無申請回鄉證，「呢啲人究竟咩心態呢？咪就係支持港獨囉，或者根本都唔去大陸，唔鍾意去」。<br />\n<br />\n他強調，「做人要有多啲選擇」，不應只有一條出路，「自己係中國人又唔承認自己身分，中國而家經濟同發展一日千里，有佢嘅好處你都唔去，陰公，有金喺嗰度執你都唔執」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171004/s00001/1507087570344\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171004%2Fs00001%2F1507087570344&d=%2Bo0wIrWmWqEUC3ikrKXdqwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=649e561e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171004%2Fs00001%2F1507087570344&h=d221592b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171004/s00001/1507087570344</a>"},{"pid":"231e62f281d4175a6536d4c0d25f1fb52c08d37b","tid":423584,"uid":1435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T04:33:51.000Z","msg":"不來四方西等成個民主黨都係港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d696ca5f3fcc0f7a4a90e9b6b3395c0747a194","tid":423584,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T04:34:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/04/123436_01e784063434ed4d8fad7be84bd34af0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F04%2F123436_01e784063434ed4d8fad7be84bd34af0.jpg&h=fd358f3b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e87c86ceed8ce5a3b1be63b485790aa3ff0f2eb","tid":423584,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T04:36:20.000Z","msg":"條友係咪曲線黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"048b69959301a6f782ed0d6f265171e27af44474","tid":423584,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T04:37:07.000Z","msg":"無知一問<br />\n<br />\n回鄉證得一條出路定係BNO 得一條出路<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}